A **powerful text-based web browser** that runs entirely in your terminal. Named after the legendary Ravana from Hindu mythology, whose 10 heads represented vast knowledge and wisdom from multiple perspectives.

**Created by: Krishna D**

[![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.8+-blue.svg)](https://www.python.org/downloads/)
[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-green.svg)](LICENSE)
[![Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/version-1.0.4-brightgreen.svg)](https://github.com/krishna182005/ravanan)
[![PyPI](https://img.shields.io/badge/pypi-ravanan-blue)](https://pypi.org/project/ravanan/)

---

## ğŸŒŸ Why Ravanan?

Ravana, the legendary scholar-king, possessed 10 heads symbolizing mastery over different dimensions of knowledge. Similarly, **Ravanan browser** offers 10 powerful capabilities for navigating the web in a unique, terminal-based way!

---

## ğŸ”± The 10 Heads of Wisdom

Like Ravana's 10 heads representing different dimensions of knowledge, this browser offers 10 powerful capabilities:

1. **ğŸŒ Smart HTML Parsing** - Extracts text, links, headers, lists, tables, and more
2. **âš¡ Fast HTTP Fetching** - Quick and efficient web page loading with full HTTPS support
3. **ğŸ¨ Beautiful Rendering** - Styled terminal output with colors and formatting
4. **ğŸ”— Link Navigation** - Jump to links by number, Lynx-style
5. **ğŸ“œ History Management** - Full back/forward browsing history
6. **ğŸ” Advanced Search** - Case-sensitive and case-insensitive search within pages
7. **âŒ Error Handling** - Graceful handling of all web errors (404, timeouts, etc.)
8. **ğŸ“Š Content Extraction** - Clean extraction of meaningful content
9. **ğŸ’ Clean Interface** - Intuitive commands and beautiful UI with responsive banner
10. **ğŸ’ª Terminal Power** - Full-featured browsing without leaving your terminal

## âœ¨ Additional Features

- ğŸ’¾ **Save Pages** - Save current page as text file
- ğŸ“Š **Statistics** - View browsing statistics
- â„¹ï¸ **Page Info** - Detailed information about current page
- ğŸ“‹ **List All Links** - Display all links on current page
- ğŸ†˜ **Comprehensive Help** - Detailed help system
- ğŸ¯ **Multiple Commands** - Many ways to accomplish the same task

